extRun SCXW203860246 BCX0\"> Words Become Your Actions, </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2Themed SCXW203860246 BCX0\">Your</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW203860246 BCX0\"> Actions Become Your Habits, </span></h5><h5><span class=\"NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2Themed SCXW203860246 BCX0\">Your</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW203860246 BCX0\"> Habits Become Your Values, </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2Themed SCXW203860246 BCX0\">Your</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW203860246 BCX0\"> Values Become Your Destiny.</span></h5><div><em><span class=\"designation SCXW35742131 BCX0\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW208200875 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" data-contrast=\"auto\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW208200875 BCX0\"> <span class=\"TextRun SCXW203860246 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" data-contrast=\"auto\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW203860246 BCX0\">Mahatma Gandhi</span></span></span></span></span></em></div></div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t",
